title: RHOC: Vikings of Wishful Thinking
description:
Vicki and Tamra are friends again on Real Housewives of Orange County. But will it last? And will Peggy ever get over the indignity of hearing vague laughter? Come join us as we wrap up the Icelandic trip with some lamb shank and marital awkwardness.

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
